<subSubSection id="7B24E35411A834AFEB7C37ED47C87D4C" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="1C8712F7FB32DF4EEA22183979BF1FC3" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FB3FCD306A073204556B59BC252A06D3" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">
This species is dedicated to the Andaki indigenous people, an American ethnic group that inhabited the upper 
<normalizedToken id="53F100F0215D0A020BA36AED243C0783" originalValue="Caquetá">Caqueta</normalizedToken>
River basin.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
